{"tid":2377048,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"繼續滅聲 民眾被「旅遊」禁受訪","createTime":"2021-01-23T09:23:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-23T09:24:56.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"9137531ab22b470e00cf8b488c416d5f2cec2302","tid":2377048,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T09:23:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210123/ESJYLFA62JBM7KXXLYAAW2HSGU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210123%2FESJYLFA62JBM7KXXLYAAW2HSGU%2F&d=m1YmCj491ZwsIKcmlD2Tam%2Fv5hJrJLSiIP9i8i%2FMgDc%3D&h=727b3424\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20210123%2FESJYLFA62JBM7KXXLYAAW2HSGU%2F&h=8e39a92a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20210123/ESJYLFA62JBM7KXXLYAAW2HSGU/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n繼續滅聲 民眾被「旅遊」禁受訪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Q2trEa-BNS5h2PvbXsv9WGDLy9U=/1469x975/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/IN5OJQ6XENHZ5OTOLWVVJZOFHI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FQ2trEa-BNS5h2PvbXsv9WGDLy9U%3D%2F1469x975%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FIN5OJQ6XENHZ5OTOLWVVJZOFHI.jpg&h=edda08d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n武漢（圖）因瞞報和禁言令全球遭殃，在封城一周年前夕，當局未吸取教訓，依然不准人發聲，不單把接受媒體訪問的居民送往外地「旅遊」七日，又警告其他人這兩天不能接受外媒採訪。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：武漢封城一周年 日記作者再呼喊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歐美促放公民記者<br />\n<br />\n有武漢公民本與本報記者約在本周進行訪問，但疑因接受其他媒體訪問並曝光後，被當局送往外地「旅遊」七日，根據本報收到的訊息，該武漢公民在被送走前表示，「馬上被旅遊，無危險，關機一周」。也有武漢人表示當局警告他，這兩天不能接受境外媒體採訪。<br />\n<br />\n去年在武漢封城時有四名公民記者前往實地記錄後被捕，包括方斌、張展、陳秋實和李澤華，當中陳和李已獲釋但未露面，張上月被判監四年。香港電台昨引述方斌的朋友透露，方的家人曾多次到派出所查詢，公安口頭回覆，方最初涉煽動顛覆國家政權罪，後改為涉嫌尋釁滋事罪，但羈押的地點無從了解。另外，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n《蘋果》記者/香港電台"},{"pid":"1ebbb2bedbd51457ddffd4424ae0c3673c2fad68","tid":2377048,"uid":17641,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-23T09:24:56.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>李文亮係漢奸，走狗，賣國賊，遺臭萬年</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}